bles\n   - Optimization-based estimators: Linear models (Bayes, GLM, LARS, Ridge), Manifold Learning (t-SNE), Neural Networks (MLP, RBM)\n   - Other: KMeans clustering, GraphicalLasso, TheilSenRegressor, NCA\n\n4. **_fit_context decorator** (sklearn/base.py): A context manager decorator that runs fit methods with appropriate validation and warning handling. It's used extensively across all estimators that have specialized fit behavior requiring careful state management.\n\nThese mechanisms work together to provide consistent, structured error handling and informative logging across scikit-learn's diverse estimator implementations."
